sinhaya ( english : lion ) is a 2016 sri lankan sinhala-language drama film written and directed by v.sivadasan and produced by sunil t.fernando for sunil t. films .   the film features ranjan ramanayake , maheshi madushanka , sanath gunathilake and duleeka marapana in the lead roles .   featuring music composed by somapala rathnayake and cinematography by sujith nishantha .   the film was released on 30 march 2016 .